---
title: Striploin Steak and Creamy Chive Sauce with Balsamic Burst Tomatoes
description: In the mood for a luxe steak dinner? Look no further! Tender striploin steak is smothered in a rich and creamy chive sauce and topped with balsamic burst tomatoes. Herbed mashed potatoes add flair and balance to tie everything together.
